</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_60_r1l7"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> eẅr freẅntlıch ſchrıft dıe Jr vns auf <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> nehſt gewerb getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l8">habt / als von der beſlıeſſung <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der antwurt der Jr vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l10">gut freẅnde vonn Stetten <expan>v̈berkome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyt etc / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l11">Vnd danken des <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt gancʒem fleıſſ / Vnd als Jr begert eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l12"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> auch ʒuuerſteen ʒu <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . Alſo tun wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l13">ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Marggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> noch nıht geant = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l14">wurt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> ſteet noch ʒu <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> als Jr von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l15"><expan>bottſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> nehſt wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> habt / Denn als Jr begert habt / ob wır ıcht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l17"><expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> lewff <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣr wıſſen etc Alſo <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wır ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıte<ex>n</ex></expan> niht <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l18">Denn daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>kawffleẅt<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>auf</expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> ıſt / Daʒ vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l19"><expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der Römıſch vnd ʒu <expan>Vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc künıg vnd ~ der künıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l20">von Polan ʒum Creẅcʒ nydwendıg kaſchaw <expan>beyeınand<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeın </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l21">vnd daʒ ſıe vnd dıe <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Preẅſſen groſſ <expan>ſamnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd volk <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l22">ſıch des ~ keyſer von Tartarn da mit aufcʒuhalten / der Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l23"><expan>bottſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> getan hab daʒ er ſıe meyne ʒu <expan>beſtreıte<ex>n</ex></expan> / wıe ſıch aber das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l24">machen wırdt / wıſſen wır nıht / denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_line_1577011399753_2452"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> v <hi rend="sup"> a </hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> dıoniſij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_60" id="29r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Ulme </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan>, ewr frewntlich schrift, die ir uns auf
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> nehst gewerb getan habt als von der
                        besliessung <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der antwurt, der ir und
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> unser gut frewnde vonn stetten
                                <expan>überkome<ex>n</ex></expan> seyt etc.,
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> und danken des
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit ganczem fleiss. Und als ir begert, ewch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> auch zu versteen zu
                            <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, also tun wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                        wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem <expan>marggraf<ex>en</ex></expan>, noch
                        niht geantwurt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> steet noch zu
                            <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>, als ir von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> nehst wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> habt. Denn als ir begert habt, ob wir
                        icht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> lewff <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣr
                        wissen etc., also <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> wir zu disen
                                <expan>zeite<ex>n</ex></expan> niht <expan>sund<ex>er</ex>s</expan>,
                        denn daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>kawfflewt<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>auf</expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> ist, daz unser
                                <expan>gnedigist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, der römisch und zu
                            <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc. künig, und der künig von Polan zum
                        Crewcz nydwendig Kaschaw <expan>beyeinand<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sein und daz sie und die
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Prewssen gross
                            <expan>samnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und volk <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        sich des keyser von Tartarn da mit aufczuhalten, der in
                                <expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> getan hab, daz er sie meyne zu
                                <expan>bestreite<ex>n</ex></expan>. Wie sich aber das machen wirdt,
                        wissen wir niht. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v <hi rend="sup"> a </hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Dionisii.</ab>
</div>
